{"tid":2166576,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"京當年逼微軟交原始碼","createTime":"2020-08-20T13:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:37:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1b1ee6a7ca4896cd887c96ba5c11dc8e74fe05","tid":2166576,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:35:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200820/S4HEXDJ2RJBETHQBY2EOTYCMPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200820%2FS4HEXDJ2RJBETHQBY2EOTYCMPY%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5QVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=781b2930\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200820%2FS4HEXDJ2RJBETHQBY2EOTYCMPY%2F&h=cfc2e07c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200820/S4HEXDJ2RJBETHQBY2EOTYCMPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n京當年逼微軟交原始碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2X4eTyAvv7TJaocJ3FwQNPcJVII=/3981x2764/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CT7UVQDLS5FVDPQM5HEEJD4LVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2X4eTyAvv7TJaocJ3FwQNPcJVII%3D%2F3981x2764%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCT7UVQDLS5FVDPQM5HEEJD4LVI.jpg&h=dfb3a58f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■微軟曾向中國政府開放產品的原始碼。<br />\n<br />\n美國宣佈封殺中國科企字節跳動（Bytedance）的手機應用程式TikTok，更強迫其要出售予微軟或美國公司，方可避免被封殺命運。內地網民就事件大罵美國此舉是「巧取豪奪」、「強搶民女」；事實上在豪奪別人東西的事情上，中國早在十多年前已經使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle拒過濾 遭封鎖<br />\n<br />\n美國科技企業早在2000年已開始進軍中國市場，如微軟、Google、蘋果公司及思科等大型科技企業，不過，中方要求這些企業交出原始碼（source code），即編寫電腦程式的文字檔案，才允許其在中國發展；意味這些公司要放棄其高度保密的架構，才能來換取內地市場。<br />\n<br />\n2007年，微軟無奈地妥協，被迫與中國信息安全產品測評認證中心簽署《安全計劃源代碼》協議，需要向中國政府開放其產品的原始碼，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n2006年，Google進軍中國時建立了「Google中國」，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n結果到最後，Google宣佈不再過濾網上搜尋結果，與中方談判失敗；2014年開始，Google的服務被中國全面封鎖。"},{"pid":"b002b9beb1e438f63f34d93bd1ae73ea427c5175","tid":2166576,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:37:15.000Z","msg":"強盗話人強盗，而家扮死狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}